{
  "stem": "1550.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My affidavit, I can't give you exact dates and so forth, when this arrived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I was in the meantime, I was trying to get-- I think I mentioned that to you I was trying to become a cabinet maker.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of my uncles knew a cabinet maker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went there and started as an apprentice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I stayed there with this cabinet maker for about six or seven months.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, in the meantime, all kinds of things happened that [INAUDIBLE] happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was trying to go to England.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was, for the Youth Aliyah the [NON-ENGLISH] Aliyah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think I was getting too old, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So, eventually, there was nothing else left for me but to wait for the-- for the affidavit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I registered with the American consulate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that takes-- that took time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You see, there were thousands and thousands of people who had also affidavits.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were only so many doctors at the American consulate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because the Americans were quite strict, you know, with tuberculosis and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was waiting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was waiting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, in the meantime, what else happened?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the way, I'd also joined one of the Zionist organizations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because that was the thing to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went even to a camp, a camp in the country.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one fine day, it's just a funny thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a camp and in the-- in the-- in the country.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a Jewish youth organization called Blau Weiss, which was blue white.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Hebrew, it was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it's associated with a labor party, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one fine day, two SS men came to inspect the local library.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
